Controls:

[1-9] to select an individual unit
Ctrl-A to select all units
Shift+[1-9] to add a unit to current selection

Right-click to interact with an object, or attack an enemy
Ctrl-right-click to use a special attack (i.e. sword guy's shield bash)

P or spacebar to pause the game

Tips:
- Pause often.  You can use this time to choose new targets for your units.
- Use the shield bash ability to defeat the wizard.
